item.title: CVE-2021-31869|2024-09-17T02:27:53.096Z -- pimcore -- pimcore%20adminbundle
item.description: Pimcore AdminBundle version 6.8.0 and earlier suffers from a SQL injection issue in the specificID variable used by the application. This issue was fixed in version 6.9.4 of the product.
